OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Then dry for a time overnight
OL,8,Fbefore some thundery rain develops
OL,9,Flater on, more especially later on.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,12,Foccasional rain, some heavy and
OL,13,Fthundery rain at times especially in
OL,14,Fthe south. Some drier spells of
OL,15,Fweather too. Warm and humid.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,18,Fstart Saturday, but cloud increasing
OL,19,Fwith showery rain later. Sunday and
OL,20,FMonday see sunny spells and showers,
OL,21,Fwith a fresh southwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
